OL,3,CMurder charge after 'much-loved' man
OL,4,Cdies in suspected hit and run
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Fafter a "much-loved" 44-year-old man
OL,8,Fwas killed in a suspected hit-and-run
OL,9,Fin a town centre.
OL,11,FMatthew Weller died in hospital after
OL,12,Fbeing struck by a Volkswagen Passat at
OL,13,Fthe junction of Blackburn Road and
OL,14,FBirch Street in Accrington shortly
OL,15,Fafter 10pm on 22 April.
OL,17,FLancashire Police said the vehicle
OL,18,Finvolved was later found abandoned on
OL,19,FBarden Road after it failed to stop at
OL,20,Fthe scene. It has since been recovered
OL,21,Ffor forensic examination.
