OL,3,CMurder charge after 'much-loved' man
OL,4,Cdies in suspected hit and run
OL,6,FPaying tribute, Matthew's family said:
OL,7,F"Matt was a much-loved son, brother,
OL,8,Fand uncle. He was a music lover and
OL,9,Fleft an impression on those that knew
OL,10,Fhim.
OL,12,F"Rest peacefully Matt, you will be
OL,13,Fmissed."
OL,15,FMuhammad Haarith, 22, of Exchange
OL,16,FStreet, Accrington, has been charged
OL,17,Fmurder following the incident and will
OL,18,Fappear at Preston Magistrates Court.
