OL,3,CMurder charge after 'much-loved' man
OL,4,Cdies in suspected hit and run
OL,6,FThree 17-year-old boys from Accrington
OL,7,Fand an 18-year-old from Blackburn who
OL,8,Fwere also arrested in connection with
OL,9,Fthe incident have been bailed pending
OL,10,Ffurther enquiries.
